msgid ""
"udpxy is an IPTV stream relay, a UDP-to-HTTP multicast traffic relay daemon "
"which forwards multicast UDP streams to HTTP clients."
msgstr ""
"Is sealaíocht srutha IPTV é udpxy, deamhan sealaíochta tráchta ilchraolta "
"UDP-go-HTTP a chuireann sruthanna ilchraolta UDP ar aghaidh chuig cliaint "
"HTTP."

